    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5268-Insights-from-the-First-Chapter-of-Durga-Saptashati.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;How to Know the Truth?&#34; /&gt;
      
